      <title>欧洲央行行长拉加德称欧盟共同融资是“可取的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-s-lagarde-says-common-eu-financing-is-desirable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，她赞成欧盟为安全、气候转型等共同利益进行联合融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-s-lagarde-says-common-eu-financing-is-desirable</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>十一月份就业报告中值得关注的内容</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-04/what-to-watch-for-in-the-november-jobs-report-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国 11 月份就业报告将于周五公布。彭博经济预计就业岗位将增加 182,000 个。华尔街预计就业岗位将增加 218,000 个。彭博经济的 Anna Wong 解释了“彭博监视”的预测。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-04/what-to-watch-for-in-the-november-jobs-report-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:06:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行通胀斗争即将结束但尚未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-s-lagarde-sees-weaker-economic-growth-and-uncertain-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行抗击通胀的斗争已接近尾声，但尚未获胜。]]></description>
