      <title>因 CSN 收购谈判失败，InterCement 申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/brazil-s-intercement-files-for-bankruptcy-as-csn-deal-fails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[资金短缺的巴西水泥制造商 InterCement Participacoes SA 在拖欠债务后向圣保罗申请破产保护，结束了与债权人数月的谈判。]]></description>
